Fuel Retailer KenolKobil Plans to Offer Discounted Gasoline, Diesel Prices

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-03-15T08:06:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-15/fuel-retailer-kenolkobil-plans-to-offer-discounted-gasoline-diesel-prices.html
KenolKobil Ltd., a Kenyan fuel
retailer with operations in seven African countries, said it
plans to offer a discount of 2 shillings per litre on gasoline
and diesel every Tuesday and Friday.  KenolKobil commented in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  